ADDITIONAL TERMS FOR CRYPTOGRAPHIC COMPONENTS

The cryptographic components of VeliKey Aegis, including but not limited to
the VELI-DEFAULT-2025 cipher suite implementation, are provided for the
benefit of the security community. While we encourage review and analysis,
please note:

1. EXPORT COMPLIANCE: Users are responsible for compliance with applicable
   export control laws and regulations.

2. PATENT NOTICE: VeliKey may seek patent protection for certain innovations.
   This license grants rights to the software implementation but does not
   grant any patent licenses. Patent licenses, if required, must be obtained
   separately.

3. TRADEMARK: The VeliKey name and logo are trademarks of VeliKey, Inc.
   This license does not grant permission to use VeliKey trademarks except
   as required for reasonable and customary use in describing the origin
   of the Software.

4. SECURITY RESEARCH: We encourage responsible security research. Please
   review our SECURITY.md file for vulnerability reporting procedures.

